Example Payment Application Requirements:

- Postgres DB: docker run --name some-postgres -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=mysecretpassword -p 5432:5432 -d postgres

- You need payment api mock service for this demo application
   url:
      http://localhost:8888/v1/payment
   response:
      {
           "responseCode": "0",
           "responseMessage": "Success"
      }

Example Request:
   {
       "name": "name",
       "surname": "surname",
       "amount": 15.00
   }
